---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 260
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=The Round of Existence
By: Sri Chandrasekhara Bhâratî Swâmigal
---
It is far better to be an animal than to be a man making no effort to
attain knowledge, for ... the animals have no sins and have no need to
expiate them.
